high_descs: Turn around and veer left and go straight to the stove.
Pick up the pot on the right burner on the stove.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the pot in the fridge to the left of the fruit. Close the door, wait a moment, and take the pot out.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Place the pot on the back right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot on a stove.

high_descs: Turn around, head to the stove on the left.
Pick up the pan on the right of the stove.
Turn around, bring the pan to the fridge.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Take the chilled pan back to the stove.
Put the pan on the back of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the rear of the kitchen.
Pick up the pot from the front right burner.
Carry the pot and turn around and locate the fridge.
Open the fridge and plate the pot inside. Shut the door. Open the door and take the pot out then shut the door.
Carry the pot and turn around to go back to the stove.
Place the pot on the far right burner.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pot and place it on the stove.

high_descs: Turn around and walk through the kitchen to the stove
Pick up the front right metal pot from the stove
Turn around and walk to the fridge
Put the pot into the fridge then remove it
Turn around and walk back over to the stove
Set the pot down on the stove's back right burner
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled pot on the stove

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the kitchen stove.
Pick up the pot on the right side of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the pot inside then close the refrigerator. Wait 5 seconds then open the refrigerator and take the pot out.
Walk over to the stove again.
Put the pot down on the back burner on the right side of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Cool down the pot on the right side of the stove.

high_descs: Walk over to the stove in the kitchen.
Pick up the pot on the right.
Carry the pot over to the fridge.
Cool the pot in the fridge, then remove it.
Go back to the stove behind you.
Place the pot on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Cool off a pot from the stove in the fridge.
